name: Global X Enhanced S&P/TSX 60 Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and net of expenses, 1.25 times (125%) the performance of an index of equity securities representing the large-cap market segment of the Canadian equity market (currently, the S&P/TSX 60 Index). The ETF will use leverage in order to seek to achieve its investment objective The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and net of expenses, 1.25 times (125) the performance of an index of equity securities representing the largecap market segment of the Canadian equity market.
